# Android WebView assets.
#
# - web/ is generated at build time by the copyWebAssets Gradle task from the
#   Vite build output (../../web/dist) — do not commit it.
# - model.tflite (the piece-tracking touch model) ships with the Board SDK
#   bundle. Copy it here from the Board developer portal / SDK before building;
#   it is intentionally not vendored in this repo.
